column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/9bf2a4aba2c22dc451ce000f7ef081b3d3562b84 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

Take 4 crayons and lay them out sideways. Next take each one starting from the left and lay them on top of each other. They will be in the same order. Now, start over but instead take them from the right and put them underneath one another. They will be in the same order.\n
